Title: Add permissions for rulesets which can have access to commandline execution
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1592911643
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

For the rulesets {{Execute MRPE checks}}, {{Plugins, local checks and MRPE for non-root users}},
{{Installation paths for agent files (Linux, UNIX)}} and {{Allowed agent access via IP address}}
you need the permission {{Can add or modiy executables}} in order to prevent code injection.
